' Load the long array
For j% = 1 To nY&
For i% = 1 To nX&
larray&(i%, j%) = RGB(pixels(1, i%, j%), pixels(2, i%, j%), pixels(3, i%, j%))

Next i%
Next j%

Exit Sub

